DIV1.P:
I suppose it was intended for a Gate or Entrance into the City;
for it fronts the great Street of the Suburbs, and has a vast Walk planted
with Trees leading from it towards Bois de Vincennes.

DIV2.P:
Of Forc't Mushroomes they have many Crops in a year;
but for the Months of August, September, October, when they
na∣turally grow in the Fields, they prepare no Artificial Beds.

Here were very many Fig-Trees well grown in square
Boxes; and Parterrs well stockt with Flowers; each sort by them∣selves;
as Tulips a-part; Junkills a-part; Anemonies a-part;
Ranunculus's a-part; Daffadills a-part.
